WEBVTT

00:00.416 --> 00:01.550
<i>My name is Michael Westen.</i>
<i>I used to be a spy until...</i>

00:04.318 --> 00:06.853
We got a burn notice
on you. You're blacklisted.

00:06.921 --> 00:09.289
<i>When you're burned,</i>
<i>you've got nothing --</i>

00:09.357 --> 00:11.958
<i>no cash, no credit,</i>
<i>no job history.</i>

00:12.026 --> 00:14.327
<i>You're stuck in whatever city</i>
<i>they decide to dump you in.</i>

00:14.395 --> 00:16.363
Where am I?
Miami.

00:16.430 --> 00:19.599
<i>You do whatever work</i>
<i>comes your way.</i>

00:19.667 --> 00:22.235
<i>You rely on anyone</i>
<i>who's still talking to you.</i>

00:22.303 --> 00:23.837
<i>A trigger-happy</i>
<i>ex-girlfriend...</i>

00:23.904 --> 00:25.472
Should we shoot them?

00:25.539 --> 00:28.041
<i>...An old friend who used</i>
<i>to inform on you to the FBI...</i>

00:28.109 --> 00:30.443
You know spies --
a bunch of bitchy little girls.

00:30.511 --> 00:32.946
<i>...Family, too...</i>
<i>Hey, is that your mom again?</i>

00:33.014 --> 00:35.115
<i>...If you're desperate.</i>
<i>Someone needs your help, Michael.</i>

00:35.182 --> 00:37.617
<i>Bottom line --</i>
<i>as long as you're burned,</i>

00:37.685 --> 00:39.286
<i>you're not going anywhere.</i>

00:45.863 --> 00:47.430
<i>When you're preparing</i>

00:47.498 --> 00:49.099
<i>to interrogate</i>
<i>a trained operative,</i>

00:49.166 --> 00:51.668
<i>the most useful information</i>
<i>isn't professional --</i>

00:51.736 --> 00:52.535
<i>it's personal.</i>

00:54.572 --> 00:56.573
<i>You need to get</i>
<i>into the target's head...</i>

00:58.943 --> 01:00.477
<i>...Understand</i>
<i>what makes him tick.</i>

01:01.545 --> 01:06.449
<i>Of course, that's easier</i>
<i>with</i> some <i>people than others.</i>

01:08.319 --> 01:10.120
Hi, Fi.

01:12.790 --> 01:14.324
You hear that,
Michael?

01:14.391 --> 01:16.726
The shooting range
is calling your name.

01:16.794 --> 01:18.561
Love to,
but Vaughn gave me homework.

01:18.629 --> 01:21.264
Today's the day.

01:21.332 --> 01:22.532
Vaughn's
checking Simon out

01:22.600 --> 01:24.300
of whatever hole
they've been keeping him in

01:24.368 --> 01:25.702
so I can have
my face-to-face.

01:25.770 --> 01:27.570
Well, I can't imagine
he'll be too thrilled

01:27.638 --> 01:29.405
to talk to the man
who put him in that hole.

01:29.473 --> 01:31.374
Who knows?
He might surprise us.

01:31.442 --> 01:34.511
As I recall,
Simon is <i>full</i> of surprises --

01:34.578 --> 01:36.379
escaping from prison,
kidnapping you,

01:36.447 --> 01:38.314
trying to blow up
half of South Beach...

01:38.382 --> 01:40.416
Leave it to you
to invite him back to Miami.

01:40.484 --> 01:43.653
He was working
with some pretty bad folks, Fi.

01:43.721 --> 01:46.556
Whatever they're hoping
to decode with Simon's bible,

01:46.624 --> 01:47.824
whatever
they're planning...

01:47.892 --> 01:49.859
Simon's the key
to all of it.

